== Welcome to the Apoidea Project ==

Secure and anonymous file sharing in Erlang.
Made by The Awesome Team at Uppsala University.

Sunshine!

PREREQUISITES:
	1. Erlang
	2. EUnit
	3. EDoc
	4. GNU Make
	
DOWNLOAD:
	$ git clone git@github.com:ephracis/Apoidea.git
	
BUILD:
	$ make
	
GENERATE DOCUMENTATION:
	$ make doc
	
RUN TESTS:
	$ make test
	
START A DRONE:
	$ make start_drone
	
START A WORKER:
	$ make start_worker
